		<title>How Do I Receive the Tax Credit</title>
		<link>http://easyenergysavingtips.com/tax-credit-for-window-film-extended/how-do-i-receive-the-tax-credit/</link>

		<title>Keep the air flowing</title>

		<title>Other Benefits of Window Film</title>
		<link>http://easyenergysavingtips.com/did-you-know-that-window-film-helps-house-plants/other-benefits-of-window-film/</link>

		<title>How HBI Developed</title>
		<link>http://easyenergysavingtips.com/smart-buildings-save-energy/how-hbi-developed/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 08 Jul 2016 21:54:38 +0000</pubDate>
